---
// Hero · DS v2 — editorial puro, sin eyebrow flotante, sin glows.
// Titular principal primero; proof como credential line con números champagne.
---

<section
  id="inicio"
  class="min-h-screen bg-bg-primary flex items-center pt-20"
>
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-32 w-full">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr] gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">

      <!-- Copy -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-8" data-reveal>

        <!-- H1: titular principal, Black weight -->
        <h1
          class="font-montserrat text-text-primary leading-tight tracking-tight m-0"
          style="font-weight: 900; font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 7vw, 5rem); line-height: 1.08; letter-spacing: -0.02em; text-wrap: balance;"
        >
          Vuelvo alcanzable lo imposible.
        </h1>

        <!-- Subtext -->
        <p
          class="font-inter text-text-secondary m-0"
          style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 46ch;"
        >
          Diseño y opero sistemas que hacen rendir a personas, empresas e instituciones. Desde adentro, codo a codo, con resultados que se miden.
        </p>

        <!-- Credential line: proof real, sin píldoras decorativas -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-4 gap-y-2">
          {[
            { text: "Ex Director General del IESS" },
            { num: "+32.000", text: "personas" },
            { num: "$10.000M", text: "administrados" },
            { text: "Fundador de CODEIS" },
          ].map((c, i) => (
            <>
              {i > 0 && (
                <span class="text-text-muted-brand select-none" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
              )}
              <span
                class="font-montserrat text-text-secondary whitespace-nowrap"
                style="font-size: 14px;"
              >
                {c.num && (
                  <b
                    class="text-champagne"
                    style="font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;"
                  >
                    {c.num}{" "}
                  </b>
                )}
                {c.text}
              </span>
            </>
          ))}
        </div>

        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-2">
          <a
            href="/trabaja-conmigo"
            class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[1.5px] text-white bg-ember px-8 py-3.5 rounded-[6px] hover:brightness-110 transition-all duration-300 whitespace-nowrap"
          >
            Trabajemos juntos
          </a>
          <a
            href="/sobre-mi"
            class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[1.5px] text-ultra-light border border-ember px-8 py-3.5 rounded-[6px] hover:bg-ember hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 whitespace-nowrap"
          >
            Conoce mi trayectoria
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Portrait -->
      <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-end" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3">
        <img
          src="/francisco-abad.jpg"
          alt="Francisco Abad"
          width="1200"
          height="1600"
          loading="eager"
          fetchpriority="high"
          class="w-full max-w-[360px] lg:max-w-[38vw]"
          style="aspect-ratio: 3/4; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(14, 23, 56, 0.40);"
        />
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
